    <item>
      <title>派拉蒙交易引发融资担忧，索尼股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/sony-shares-fall-as-offer-for-paramount-spurs-financing-concerns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[索尼集团公司 (Sony Group Corp.) 收购派拉蒙全球公司 (Paramount Global) 的提议引发融资担忧后，其股价创下近三个月来最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/sony-shares-fall-as-offer-for-paramount-spurs-financing-concerns</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 02:47:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚马逊承诺投入 90 亿美元，将新加坡云服务投入翻倍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/amazon-to-invest-9-billion-in-singapore-to-expand-cloud-infrastructure-amzn</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚马逊公司计划斥资 90 亿美元扩建其在新加坡的云计算基础设施，这是最新一家加大在东南亚投资力度的全球科技公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/amazon-to-invest-9-billion-in-singapore-to-expand-cloud-infrastructure-amzn</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 02:46:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波音 Starliner 发射因火箭问题而推迟</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/boeing-starliner-launch-is-postponed-due-to-issue-with-rocket</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于运载飞船进入轨道的火箭出现技术问题，波音公司 Starliner 太空舱的历史性首次载人飞行任务在发射前推迟了几个小时。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/boeing-starliner-launch-is-postponed-due-to-issue-with-rocket</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 01:08:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>MercadoLibre 被阿根廷银行指控“滥用行为”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/banks-accuse-mercadolibre-s-fintech-arm-of-abusive-conduct</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷银行周一对 MercadoLibre Inc. 提起法律诉讼，指控其在数字支付平台上存在“滥用行为”，在央行新法规对金融科技行业实施重大变革后，该公司面临的压力加大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/banks-accuse-mercadolibre-s-fintech-arm-of-abusive-conduct</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 22:06:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
